 overlooked, contributor to Western vegan thought.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aAnimal rightszIreland. 0aAnimalsxSocial aspectszIreland. 0aVeganismxSocial aspectszIreland. 4aCultural Studies : Food. 4aEnvironmental Studies : Ecofeminist. 4aPhilosophy : Animal Rights. 4aPhilosophy : Feminist Philosophy. 4aSociology : Sociology. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143848436540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438484365423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438484365/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles